    <item>
      <title>Eyes On The Ground</title>
      <link>/wiaposts/eyes-on-the-ground/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2019 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author>
      <guid>/wiaposts/eyes-on-the-ground/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;
    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img class=&#34;my-0 rounded-md&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;/assets/images/wiapost/5095-Eyes-On-The-Ground.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Eyes On The Ground&#34; /&gt;
      
    &lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;h1 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Eyes On The Ground 
    &lt;div id=&#34;eyes-on-the-ground&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;
        &lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34;
            style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#eyes-on-the-ground&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Whether I walk, jog or run  &lt;br&gt;
If I have continuous eyes on the ground  &lt;br&gt;
I will not fall because of environmental reasons.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I may still fall but the cause will be  &lt;br&gt;
either my weak limbs or my foolishness.  &lt;br&gt;
But I am happy with this,  &lt;br&gt;
because I am in control  &lt;br&gt;
and I know my happiness  &lt;br&gt;
and miseries are 100% my doing.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
